articles.author: Daniel Cooper
articles.title: Apple's rivals aren't happy about its EU App Store changes - Engadget
articles.description: Apple has laid down the rules for opening a competing app store. It's not pleased too many of its rivals.
articles.content: Last year, the European Union implemented new laws to make big tech open up its platforms to competitors. The deadline for compliance is March, and all eyes were on how Apple, which is famous for not… [+7410 chars]
